{"tid":1761911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尹兆堅質疑政府為何不援助大專生 教育局：大學生原本已經有資助","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T08:48:17.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c9c58d7b65d48a48695bf4dc2ef70ccd654cb2","tid":1761911,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會審議一系列減輕市民財政負擔和支持香港企業的措施，涉及撥款約216億元。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨尹兆堅批評政府出手極低，又提到政府指出不援助大專生的原因是大專生原本已經有資助，在有關邏輯下，今次所有措施都不應獲得通過，因為公屋租戶、綜援人士等原本已有資助。<br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮表示，今次措施目的是協助家長紓緩經濟負擔，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申大學生已有助學金、貸款資助，強調議員可以不同意有關意見，但有關原因是政府的考慮</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府早前撤回涉及三間大學的撥款申請，民建聯蔣麗芸認為形容香港經濟將踏入寒冬，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該用儲備改善民生，而非興建美輪美奐的大樓、設施，指寧願將有關撥款用作資助大學生學費</span>。她又提到理大被發現有數千枝汽油彈，若爆炸將會把理大夷為平地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495132-20191129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495132-20191129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=43efa755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495132-20191129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=adbcd4a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495132-20191129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"49c73d6ea3a59d71e0de17bc75acd7a3b995b5cd","tid":1761911,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"蔣麗芸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e70f5e361f4b1d12c5dac991974f46b0e14fc7b","tid":1761911,"uid":131323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"應該拎去買多d tg就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1655b1e86e6dd879df4d6922d7229bbba9be078","tid":1761911,"uid":13149,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b1c9c58d7b65d48a486